Package uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.operation.impl.export.localfile

Class ImportFromLocalFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.operation.impl.export.localfile.ImportFromLocalFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, Export, GetExport, Output<Iterable<String>>, Operation
    public class ImportFromLocalFile
extends Object
implements GetExport, Output<Iterable<String>>
    An ImportFromLocalFile GetExport operation gets exported Set results. The Set export is maintained per single Job or OperationChain only. It cannot be used across multiple separate operation requests. So ExportToSet and ImportFromLocalFile must be used inside a single operation chain.
